---
title: Quick Lebanese Chicken with Body Boosting Veggies
description: We heard a good analogy recently. Putting sugary, processed foods into your body is like throwing tissue paper on a fire. A big burst of energy then puff the flames go out. Sweet potatoes on the other hand are more like throwing on a hefty log. They’re slow burning and keep you going for hours. With warming shawarma spices this is a plateful of ‘central eating’.
